title: Sikhao nongamwn Ang, khaonw fwiyakwi
lyrics:
Sikhao nongamwn Ang, khaonw fwiyakwi
Thungri lanan angkhou naigirbainw
Harsing fwidwngmwn ang, papni songsarao
Jiuni lamakhou dinthi langnw -2
Ha . . . . . . . . . . Ho . . . . . . . . . .
(A)
Jwnwmni jiukhou, krushjwng sujunan
Sohaibai jwbthi saja -2
“Papi subungni thakwi”-2
(B)
Saiko jadwngmwn, swrgw Bifajwng
Buhumao dukhu swinw -2
“Papi subungni thakwi”-2
